aim for a 10.5 per cent initial gross yield. Dividends can be paid gross
because of the fund's offshore status. The fund will have a single pricing
structure - the equivalent of the conventional unit trust bid-offer spread
is the initial charge of 5.25 per cent. The annual charge is 1 per cent;
minimum investment Pounds 1,000.
