concern. Together, they control Sofin, a private company which has run
Seleco since 1989.
However, formal control of Seleco has remained with REL, a company set up in
the early 1980s to save troubled consumer electronics groups following an
industry crisis. Seleco, formerly part of the Zanussi group, came under the
control of REL in 1983.
